# Forge automatically loads .env from the working directory

# =============================================================================
# HYPERLANE CLI (Local Development)
# =============================================================================
# SAFE TO COMMIT: This is Anvil Account 9's well-known hardcoded test key.
# See: https://book.getfoundry.sh/reference/anvil/#default-accounts
#
# Why Account 9? We use it for Hyperlane infrastructure deployments so that
# Account 0's nonces stay clean for deterministic SWR contract addresses.
# The pre-deployed Hyperlane state in .anvil-state/ was created with this key.
#
# To deploy Hyperlane: HYP_KEY=$(grep HYP_KEY packages/contracts/.env | cut -d= -f2) hyperlane core deploy
HYP_KEY=0x2a871d0798f97d79848a013d4936a73bf4cc922c825d33c1cf7073dff6d409c6

# =============================================================================
# HYPERLANE MAILBOX ADDRESSES (from `hyperlane core deploy`)
# =============================================================================
# Must match: apps/web/src/lib/contracts/crosschain-addresses.ts
#
# Local (Anvil): Deployed by Account 9, deterministic addresses
# Testnet/Mainnet: Use official Hyperlane deployment addresses
HUB_MAILBOX=
SPOKE_MAILBOX=

